âœ… Step 4: Launch EC2 Instances in Each Subnet
Youâ€™ll repeat these steps for each of the 5 subnets in the Production VPC:

ğŸ”§ Steps to Launch an EC2 Instance:
Go to the EC2 Console â†’ click â€œLaunch Instanceâ€

Fill in the following details:

